  37,10,But whoever manages to stealthily eavesdrop is ňĻinstantlyňļ pursued by a piercing flare
  37,11,"So ask them ňĻO Prophetňļ, which is harder to create: them or other marvels of Our creation?¬†Indeed, We created them from a sticky clay"
