  40,77,"So be patient ňĻO Prophetňļ. Surely Allah‚Äôs promise is true. Whether We show you some of what We threaten them with, or cause you to die ňĻbefore thatňļ, to Us they will ňĻallňļ be returned"
  40,78,"We already sent messengers before you. We have told you the stories of some of them, while others We have not. It was not for any messenger to bring a sign without Allah‚Äôs permission. But when Allah‚Äôs decree comes, judgment will be passed with fairness, and the people of falsehood will then be in ňĻtotalňļ loss"
  40,79,It is Allah Who made cattle for you so that you may ride some and eat others
  40,80,"Also, you find in them ňĻotherňļ benefits.¬†And by means of them you may reach destinations you desire. And you are carried upon ňĻsome ofňļ them and upon ships"
  40,81,And He shows you His signs. Now which of Allah‚Äôs signs will you deny
  40,82,"Have they not travelled throughout the land to see what was the end of those who were ňĻdestroyedňļ before them? They were far superior in might and ňĻricher inňļ monuments throughout the land, but their ňĻworldlyňļ gains were of no benefit to them"
