  41,9,"Ask ňĻthem, O Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúHow can you disbelieve in the One Who created the earth in two Days? And how can you set up equals with Him? That is the Lord of all worlds"
  41,10,"He placed on the earth firm mountains, standing high, showered His blessings upon it, and ordained ňĻallňļ its means of sustenance‚ÄĒtotaling four Days exactly‚ÄĒfor all who ask"
