  43,69,ňĻthoseňļ who believed in Our signs and ňĻfullyňļ submitted ňĻto Usňļ
  43,70,"Enter Paradise, you and your spouses, rejoicing.‚ÄĚ"
  43,71,Golden trays and cups will be passed around to them. There will be whatever the souls desire and the eyes delight in. And you will be there forever
  43,72,That is the Paradise which you will be awarded for what you used to do
