  45,6,These are Allah‚Äôs revelations which We recite to you ňĻO Prophetňļ in truth. So what message will they believe in after ňĻdenyingňļ Allah and His revelations
  45,7,Woe to every sinful liar
  45,8,"They hear Allah‚Äôs revelations recited to them, then persist ňĻin denialňļ arrogantly as if they did not hear them. So give them good news of a painful punishment"
  45,9,"And whenever they learn anything of Our revelations, they make a mockery of it. It is they who will suffer a humiliating punishment"
